{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr verehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.160", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu sp\u00e4ter Stunde behandeln wir einen doch sehr wichtigen Antrag zur Entlastung der deutschen Unternehmerschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere des kleinen Mittelstandes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vom B\u00fcrokratieaufwand. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der B\u00fcrokratieaufwand der deutschen Unternehmen f\u00fcr Berichtspflichten an den deutschen Staat betr\u00e4gt nahezu 50\u00a0Milliarden Euro pro Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle wollen hier Erleichterungen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Parteien leider oftmals nur in ihren Sonntagsreden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.520", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Verb\u00e4nde in ihren Wahlpr\u00fcfsteinen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.800", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dadurch belastet sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.520", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von ihrer eigentlichen Arbeit abgehalten werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Antrag ist ein Schritt in diese Richtung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerhard Schr\u00f6der hat mit seiner Agenda\u00a02010 einen Beitrag zur wirtschaftlichen Entwicklung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.200", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Beitrag zum seit langem tragenden Aufschwung in dieser Republik geleistet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.440", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings hat er mit der sogenannten Vorf\u00e4lligkeit der Sozialversicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge dem deutschen Mittelstand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den deutschen Unternehmen einen B\u00e4rendienst erwiesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Aktion im Jahr\u00a02006\u00a0 20\u00a0Milliarden Euro Kosten f\u00fcr die Unternehmerschaft verursacht hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.480", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die geschultert worden sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.640", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deshalb noch einmal meinen ausdr\u00fccklichen Dank an die Unternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das geleistet und ertragen haben\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute haben wir immer noch eine immense B\u00fcrokratie zu schultern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Unternehmer sind gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am sechstletzten Tag des Monats eine Sch\u00e4tzung vorzunehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie denn der Monat ausl\u00e4uft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jedes Unternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das mit variablen Kosten arbeitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit St\u00fcckkosten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stundenl\u00f6hnen oder Akkordl\u00f6hnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss einsch\u00e4tzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.880", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie der Monat ausgeht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.080", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt eine kleine b\u00fcrokratische Erleichterung insofern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als man inzwischen auf Basis des Vormonats sch\u00e4tzen darf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.480", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es bleibt dabei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man nach dieser Sch\u00e4tzung nat\u00fcrlich eine vern\u00fcnftige, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine auf den tats\u00e4chlichen Ergebnissen basierende Abrechnung im Folgemonat nachreichen muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.640", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der kleine Handwerksmeister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.600", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der wenige Angestellte hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.760", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Gewerbetreibende mit wenigen Angestellten muss 24 statt 12\u00a0Abrechnungen im Jahr machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wann macht er sie? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.560", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meist am Wochenende unter Aufgabe seiner Freizeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seiner Familienzeit und der Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.200", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die allen anderen in diesem Land zugestanden wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um sich auch einmal zu erholen oder mit anderen Dingen zu befassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.800", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Mittelstand \u00e4chzt da unter b\u00fcrokratischer Last."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.240", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Normenkontrollrat sch\u00e4tzt in seinem Abschlussbericht allein den Aufwand f\u00fcr diese 24 statt 12\u00a0Meldungen auf circa 1,5\u00a0Milliarden Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Absurdit\u00e4t der deutschen B\u00fcrokratie widerspiegelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenso wie viele andere: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Mindestdokumentationspflichten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Lohngleichheitsgesetz sowie die Dokumentation flexibler Arbeitszeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.840", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allein seit dem Jahr\u00a02011 ist der b\u00fcrokratische Aufwand in diesem Land um fast 10\u00a0Milliarden Euro gestiegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.040", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit muss Schluss sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Normenkontrollrat fordert einen KMU-Test, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine \u00dcberpr\u00fcfung genau dieser F\u00e4lligkeiten und b\u00fcrokratischen Lasten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.840", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.360", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit diesem Antrag fordern wir einen Systemwechsel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.840", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt das umsatzsteuerrechtliche Instrument der sogenannten Sondervorauszahlung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie versetzt die Unternehmen in die Lage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die b\u00fcrokratische Last durch eine j\u00e4hrliche Sondervorauszahlung abzubauen und die Meldungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.280", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Zahlungspflicht in den Folgemonat zu verschieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.720", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man exakt wei\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.960", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie der Monat gelaufen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viele Stunden die Arbeitnehmer geleistet haben und wie viel Ertrag in der Firma angekommen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hiermit beseitigen wir das langj\u00e4hrige \u00c4rgernis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "24 statt 12\u00a0Abrechnungen pro Jahr machen zu m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.920", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re ein gro\u00dfer Schritt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.240", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit entlasten wir gerade die kleinen und mittelst\u00e4ndischen Unternehmen sp\u00fcrbar,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es kostet die Sozialversicherungstr\u00e4ger und uns alle keinen Cent."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.720", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir schlagen eine Lichtung in den deutschen B\u00fcrokratiedschungel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.920", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns damit anfangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.480", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt keinen parteipolitischen Grund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.760", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diesen Antrag abzulehnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.040", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.440", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner ist der Kollege Max Straubinger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.000", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "CDU/CSU."
   ]
  }
 ]
}